3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper mentions the performance of forwarding protocols, which involves the use of data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper discusses the behavior of mobile agents in a small world, which is a topic in multiagent systems. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper presents a model for predicting the performance of forwarding protocols, which involves system analysis and control.
